dan istirahat dulu.

253
00:22:45,950 --> 00:22:47,580
Sekarang belum tengah malam.

254
00:22:47,580 --> 00:22:50,050
Apalagi, lukamu belum pulih.

255
00:22:50,400 --> 00:22:51,620
Aku tak boleh lalai bertugas.

256
00:22:51,710 --> 00:22:53,050
Kusuruh pulang, maka pulanglah.

257
00:22:53,280 --> 00:22:54,290
Ini perintah.

258
00:22:59,480 --> 00:23:00,100
Baik.

259
00:23:08,520 --> 00:23:10,290
Ada yang berjaga di depan pintu.

260
00:23:10,600 --> 00:23:12,500
Tentu saja Cheng Cheng
tak berani masuk.

261
00:23:33,240 --> 00:23:34,460
Sekarang sudah beres.

262
00:24:29,310 --> 00:24:32,130
Dia menutupi kesalahanku,
