263
00:24:32,710 --> 00:24:34,130
Dia yang terluka.

264
00:24:34,830 --> 00:24:36,860
Namun, kenapa hatiku
yang merasa sakit?

265
00:24:37,910 --> 00:24:39,980
Apa aku harus pergi ke sana?

266
00:24:50,600 --> 00:24:52,930
Dasar Mo Liancheng,
kenapa masih belum datang?

267
00:24:54,120 --> 00:24:55,460
Apa perkiraanku salah?

268
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:57,740
Trik ini tak berguna?

269
00:25:04,600 --> 00:25:05,580
