294
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:44,650
Minumlah sup ini.

295
00:26:50,310 --> 00:26:52,930
Yanchen sangat menyukainya.

296
00:26:53,240 --> 00:26:55,530
Dia juga berhasil
dalam ujian bela diri.

297
00:26:55,760 --> 00:26:57,170
