305
00:27:08,600 --> 00:27:11,050
Setelah tertangkap,
dia dicambuk di depan umum.

306
00:27:11,480 --> 00:27:12,980
Mencuri resep obat?

307
00:27:14,550 --> 00:27:16,620
Qu Tan'er sungguh serakah.

308
00:27:17,120 --> 00:27:18,890
Yanchen masih saja
begitu menyukainya.

309
00:27:19,240 --> 00:27:20,380
Sungguh dungu.

310
00:27:20,760 --> 00:27:23,010
Tuan Muda Mo hanya
memikirkan cintanya dulu.

311
00:27:23,120 --> 00:27:25,340
Dia pasti akan bisa melihat
sifat aslinya nanti.

312
00:27:27,520 --> 00:27:30,500
Selama latihan bela diri, Qu Tan'er
selalu sangat kompetitif.

313
00:27:30,830 --> 00:27:32,880
