mungkin akan menderita.

337
00:29:46,160 --> 00:29:47,100
Mo Liancheng.

338
00:29:47,280 --> 00:29:49,380
Kenapa pagi ini kau
tak memberi salam padaku?

339
00:29:55,360 --> 00:29:57,290
Hari ini aku tak enak badan.

340
00:29:57,360 --> 00:29:58,620
Mohon Tuan Putri memaklumi.

341
00:30:03,520 --> 00:30:04,700
Lain kali, harus ingat.

342
00:30:18,400 --> 00:30:19,380
Mo Liancheng.

343
00:30:22,600 --> 00:30:25,740
