353
00:31:10,400 --> 00:31:11,860
Di kamarku masih ada sisa.

354
00:31:11,860 --> 00:31:14,200
Kenapa selalu aku
yang lebih emosi?

355
00:31:22,240 --> 00:31:25,620
Xiaotan, apa menurutmu
cara kita ini berguna?

356
00:31:27,030 --> 00:31:29,410
Sekarang kelihatannya
tak berguna.

357
00:31:30,640 --> 00:31:32,620
Kalau begitu, terpaksa
gunakan cara terakhir.

358
00:31:34,120 --> 00:31:35,890
Aku akan mencari selingkuhan.

359
00:31:36,100 --> 00:31:37,750
Kita lihat dia bisa
diam saja atau tidak.

360
00:31:38,070 --> 00:31:40,380
Jing Xin, suruh
Mo Yanchen menemuiku.

361
00:31:50,950 --> 00:31:52,050
Sudah datang.

362
00:31:55,910 --> 00:31:56,770
Yanchen.

363
00:31:59,310 --> 00:32:00,050
Tuan Putri.

364
00:32:00,430 --> 00:32:02,050
Tak perlu beri hormat, duduklah.

365
00:32:03,030 --> 00:32:03,770
Baik.

366
00:32:08,400 --> 00:32:09,260
Jing Xin.

367
00:32:09,310 --> 00:32:11,340
Kau tak diperlukan lagi
di sini, pergilah.

368
00:32:13,830 --> 00:32:14,620
Baik.

369
00:32:20,400 --> 00:32:22,520
