378
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:00,340
Ayo.

379
00:33:01,640 --> 00:33:02,700
Makan.

380
00:33:20,760 --> 00:33:22,700
Tak apa-apa, aku sendiri saja.

381
00:33:22,760 --> 00:33:24,170
Aku sendiri saja.

